      <description>&lt;p&gt;Huawei 早陣子就宣佈在香港推出 WATCH 及 Fit 系列的全新錶款，分別是 WATCH 5，以及 Fit 4 和 Fit 4 Pro。今日這 3 款系列新錶就正式賣街，Edward 亦有前往 Huawei 位於沙田新城市廣場的分店，看看首賣情況，並直擊第一位入手新錶的顧客及作了簡短傾談，瞭解了她為何會入手 Huawei 今次的新錶。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;甫開門已有人問津&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;今日是 Huawei WATCH 5、Fit 4 及 Fit 4 Pro 的開售日，沙田店準時早上 11 時正式開門，未料開門後不足 10 分鐘已開始有兩三位客人進店瞭解 Huawei 數款新錶的入手資料，而店內亦早已擺放了三隻新錶的陳列品及所有相關錶帶供顧客上手體驗。之後筆者亦在店內直擊入手新錶的首名顧客黃小姐，她入手了綠色版本的 WATCH Fit 4 Pro。她表示之前看到相關廣告，覺得綠色版的 WATCH Fit 4 Pro 的顏色十分漂亮，所以心動想入手。今日見到實物更是喜歡 Huawei 的錶盤設計，所以最終決定「課金」。她表示之前使用其他品牌的智能手錶，要左轉右轉先找到 APP，使用上不夠 user friendly，因此今次想入手 Huawei 的新錶體驗一下。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1309516 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110032-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110032-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110032.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲今日是 Huawei WATCH 5、WATCH Fit 4 Pro 及 WATCH Fit 4 三隻新錶的開售日，未開門已見職員放好相關宣傳物。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110200-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110200-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110200.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110149-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110149-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110149.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲枱面亦擺放好三隻新錶的陳列品供顧客親身體驗。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110228-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110228-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110228.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309522" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110214-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110214-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110214.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲所有行貨有售錶帶亦有陳列出來方便用家上手感受質感。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110536-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110536-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110536.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲最難得是 WATCH 5 展示了皮（左）及鈦金屬（右）錶帶，想入手的準用家不妨先去上手感受一下。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110747-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110747-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110747.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲開店不用 10 分鐘已有顧客進店瞭解新錶，可見 Huawei 這 3 款新錶均頗受用家期待。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110749-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110749-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110749.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲而首名入手新錶的黃小姐就表示，今次入手的是綠色的 Huawei WATCH Fit 4 Pro，主要原因是：「顏色好靚！」另外錶盤設計精美及易用亦是入手主因。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;三新錶均設開售優惠&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;另外，今次 Huawei 三款新錶均設有開售優惠，當中 WATCH 5 就會附送 Huawei FreeBuds 5 無線耳機及智能體脂磅，而 WATCH Fit 4 Pro 就會附送 FreeBuds SE 2 無線耳機及智能體脂磅，而最平的 WATCH Fit 4 亦同樣會附送智能體脂磅，全部禮品均數量有限送完即止。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110315-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110315-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110315.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt; &lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1309528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110320-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110320-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/img20250530110320.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
